{"tid":2509374,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"樣衰毒撚圍爐 召集矮柒毒核突垃圾男人","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:50:35.000Z","uid":389670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0667e11e04428ac138f7cbec211118ced90b562","tid":2509374,"uid":389670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"作為亞洲樣衰第一人<br />\n從細個開始就極度樣衰<br />\n一直到而家二十頭 仲係成個垃圾毒撚咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我其實好好奇 有冇人係同我一樣咁樣衰呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎一啲同我一樣又矮又醜<br />\n而且冇錢整容嘅人<br />\n一齊入嚟呢個po圍爐<br />\n等我知道我唔係孤獨嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbjUYe2zkgFRjMToJowDzFu9DJrHKHorLb9mfWqzKR3z3?filename=cAQ7kgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAQ7kgX.jpg&h=f450e561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw黃之鋒其實好無辜 咁樣被人拖埋落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6558a55f67aa2b70cb11731e19025c97503290cf","tid":2509374,"uid":327749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9edf9c7fb416cff57cded1167047d00f70af68","tid":2509374,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"咩都唔好講 攬住我"},{"pid":"f49b9a2bd4ccef7ccb2b6f4bce270e7eb2a4ec04","tid":2509374,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" 